   [logonist126wx40h.gif] NIST Laboratory Programs Focusing on
   Nanotechnology
   "NIST will provide the new measurements, standards, and data needed to
   turn fundamental nanotechnology discoveries into new technologies,
   products and services broadly affecting our economy and our lives."
     __________________________________________________________________

   [logoDARPA144wx90h.gif]
   DARPA (main),
   The Defense Advanced Research Projects Agency (DARPA) is the central
   research and development organization for the Department of Defense
   (DoD).
   DARPA (upc)
   "Alnis is pursuing an innovative approach to the synthesis of
   nano-structures and macromolecular networks that can recognize and bind
   pathogen related compounds or antigens."
   DARPA (mto)
