   [logoairforce100wx107h.gif] AFRL
   "...The mission of AFRL is to lead the discovery, development, and
   integration of affordable warfighting technologies for our aerospace
   forces. Our mission is executed by our nine technology directorates
   located throughout the United States, the Air Force Office of
   Scientific Research, and our central staff..."
   Brigadier General Paul Nielsen, commander of the Air Force Research Lab
   .
